Total, in partnership with Bajaj Auto, recently unveiled a new lubricant for motorbikes at Villa Rosa Kempinski. 'Total Hi-Perf-Bajaj' lubricant is designed to cut operational and maintenance costs. Total Kenya lubricants commercial manager Francois Ruenes said the product will create great savings and improve livelihoods. Present was Total Kenya MD Olagoke Aluko. Kenya has an estimated 800,000 boda bodas, as motorcycles are now known.